===========================================================================

Commons-IO:

mkdir -p ~/java/apache
cd ~/java/apache
wget http://mirrors.koehn.com/apache//commons/io/binaries/commons-io-2.5-bin.tar.gz
tar zxvf commons-io-2.5-bin.tar.gz
ln -s commons-io-2.5 commons-io

===========================================================================

Axis (Apache SOAP):

http://ws.apache.org/axis/java/install.html

cd ~/tmp
wget http://mirrors.isc.org/pub/apache/ws/axis/1_3/axis-src-1_3.tar.gz
tar xzf axis-src-1_3.tar.gz
cd ~/tmp/axis-src-1_3

